        "title": "Count on grid class",
        "body": "The count on grid class not works with a count_cfg like this:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n    \"tables\": [\r\n        \"bbn_tasks\",\r\n    ],\r\n    \"fields\": {\r\n        0: \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n        1: \"bbn_tasks.type\",\r\n        2: \"bbn_tasks.id_parent\",\r\n        3: \"bbn_tasks.id_user\",\r\n        4: \"bbn_tasks.title\",\r\n        5: \"bbn_tasks.state\",\r\n        6: \"bbn_tasks.priority\",\r\n        7: \"bbn_tasks.id_alias\",\r\n        8: \"bbn_tasks.creation_date\",\r\n        9: \"bbn_tasks.deadline\",\r\n        10: \"bbn_tasks.price\",\r\n        11: \"bbn_tasks.private\",\r\n        12: \"bbn_tasks.active\",\r\n        \"close_date\": \"MAX(log_close.chrono)\",\r\n        \"close_user\": \"log_close.id_user\",\r\n        \"approve_date\": \"MAX(log_approve.chrono)\",\r\n        \"approve_user\": \"log_approve.id_user\",\r\n        \"price_date\": \"MAX(log_price.chrono)\",\r\n    },\r\n    \"order\": [\r\n        {\r\n            \"field\": \"close_date\",\r\n            \"dir\": \"DESC\",\r\n        },\r\n    ],\r\n    \"join\": [\r\n        {\r\n            \"table\": \"bbn_tasks_invoices\",\r\n            \"type\": \"left\",\r\n            \"on\": {\r\n                \"conditions\": [\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"bbn_tasks_invoices.id_task\",\r\n                        \"exp\": \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n                    },\r\n                ],\r\n            },\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            \"table\": \"bbn_tasks_logs\",\r\n            \"alias\": \"log_close\",\r\n            \"on\": {\r\n                \"conditions\": [\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"log_close.id_task\",\r\n                        \"exp\": \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n                    },\r\n                ],\r\n            },\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            \"table\": \"bbn_tasks_logs\",\r\n            \"alias\": \"log_approve\",\r\n            \"on\": {\r\n                \"conditions\": [\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"log_approve.id_task\",\r\n                        \"exp\": \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n                    },\r\n                ],\r\n            },\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            \"table\": \"bbn_tasks_logs\",\r\n            \"alias\": \"log_price\",\r\n            \"type\": \"left\",\r\n            \"on\": {\r\n                \"conditions\": [\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"log_price.id_task\",\r\n                        \"exp\": \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n                    },\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"log_price.action\",\r\n                        \"value\": \"39c2044a7c6911e89b35005056014c9f\",\r\n                    },\r\n                ],\r\n            },\r\n        },\r\n    ],\r\n    \"group_by\": [\r\n        \"bbn_tasks.id\",\r\n    ],\r\n    \"having\": {\r\n        \"conditions\": [\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"close_date\",\r\n                \"operator\": \">\",\r\n                \"exp\": \"approve_date\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"logic\": \"OR\",\r\n                \"conditions\": [\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"price_date\",\r\n                        \"operator\": \"isnull\",\r\n                    },\r\n                    {\r\n                        \"field\": \"approve_date\",\r\n                        \"operator\": \">\",\r\n                        \"exp\": \"price_date\",\r\n                    },\r\n                ],\r\n            },\r\n        ],\r\n    },\r\n    \"limit\": 25,\r\n    \"start\": 0,\r\n    \"where\": {\r\n        \"conditions\": [\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"bbn_tasks_invoices.id_invoice\",\r\n                \"operator\": \"isnull\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"bbn_tasks.state\",\r\n                \"value\": \"0cf784a5025011e8beb3005056014c9f\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"bbn_tasks.price\",\r\n                \"operator\": \"isnotnull\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"log_close.action\",\r\n                \"value\": \"05d8d426025011e8beb3005056014c9f\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"log_approve.action\",\r\n                \"value\": \"126a39537c6911e89b35005056014c9f\",\r\n            },\r\n            {\r\n                \"field\": \"bbn_tasks.active\",\r\n                \"value\": 1,\r\n            },\r\n        ],\r\n    },\r\n    \"count\": true,\r\n}\r\n```\r\nThe DB error:\r\n```text\r\n---------------------------------- DB MESSAGE -----------------------------------\r\nSQLSTATE[42S22]: Column not found: 1054 Unknown column 'close_date' in 'having clause'\r\n------------------------------------- QUERY -------------------------------------\r\nSELECT COUNT(DISTINCT bbn_tasks.id)\r\nFROM `apst_app`.`bbn_tasks`\r\n  LEFT JOIN `apst_app`.`bbn_tasks_invoices`\r\n    ON \r\n    `bbn_tasks_invoices`.`id_task` = bbn_tasks.id\r\n  JOIN `apst_app`.`bbn_tasks_logs` AS `log_close`\r\n    ON log_close.id_task = bbn_tasks.id\r\n  JOIN `apst_app`.`bbn_tasks_logs` AS `log_approve`\r\n    ON log_approve.id_task = bbn_tasks.id\r\n  LEFT JOIN `apst_app`.`bbn_tasks_logs` AS `log_price`\r\n    ON log_price.id_task = bbn_tasks.id\r\n    AND log_price.action = ?\r\nWHERE \r\n`bbn_tasks_invoices`.`id_invoice` IS NULL\r\nAND `bbn_tasks`.`state` = ?\r\nAND `bbn_tasks`.`price` IS NOT NULL\r\nAND log_close.action = ?\r\nAND log_approve.action = ?\r\nAND `bbn_tasks`.`active` = ?\r\n  HAVING close_date > approve_date\r\n  AND (price_date IS NULL\r\n    OR approve_date > price_date\r\n  )\r\n------------------------------------ VALUES -------------------------------------\r\n39c2044a7c6911e89b35005056014c9f\r\n0cf784a5025011e8beb3005056014c9f\r\n05d8d426025011e8beb3005056014c9f\r\n126a39537c6911e89b35005056014c9f\r\n1\r\n```\r\n\r\nExample: https:\/\/apstapp2.thomas.lan\/billing\/page\/tasks",
