        "title": "get_derniere_date",
        "body": "Yesterday there was a bug on the fiche pdf and dernier_kbis and other properties where printed as uid instead of dates.\r\n\r\nthe problem came from the function __pad->get_derniere_date, the one below is the picture of the function get_derniere_date yesterday.\r\n\r\n![image](\/attachments\/5f5cc4ad-08d2-493a-914d-a980785b6a92)\r\n\r\nObviously the first thing I corrected in the function was to get the uid of the type_document basing on the argument $type and not on the code '29'. \r\n\r\nAs you can see the field requested to select_one was given as 'field' and not 'fields'. Leaving 'field' in the function I obtain as result of the function an uid and not a date. Changing the word 'field' with 'fields' I have the correct result I expect from the function. The function now is:\r\n\r\n![image](\/attachments\/d23c2318-1fc7-4b52-8d9b-30305a86ff07)\r\n",
