        "title": "Sent files on pad class (from depot)",
        "body": "Currently, into the pad class, the number of the sent files has to correspond to the number of the files present into document's configuration.\r\n\r\nEx. The liasse, this is the document's configuration:\r\n\r\n![image](\/attachments\/fc2490a1-841b-4d8d-9447-ee0ef28fbb69)\r\n\r\nThe EDI file is required only in the case of sending the liasse in edi mode (plus the pdf file). In the other two modes (r\u00e9el and semplifi\u00e9), only the pdf file is required, so the insert will fail.\r\n\r\n![image](\/attachments\/59d1358c-0f24-46c0-9c8f-fb58b2385d8e)\r\n\r\nThe pad_files method is called into pad_maj method\r\n\r\n![image](\/attachments\/2f5e2e96-c046-4ea9-a710-6bb062447ca1)",
